-- McDonald's McNuggets Under Watch by China Food Administration on Additives
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-07T00:58:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/mcdonald-s-mcnuggets-under-watch-by-china-food-administration-on-additives.html

          
          
             China’s State Food and Drug
Administration is monitoring McDonald’s China Co.’s McNuggets as
the product contains the chemicals tertiary butylhydroquinone
and dimethylpolysiloxane.  
 The additives are allowed in meat products in limited
amounts, the administration said in a statement on its website.  
